O. heterotomus
], Czech Republic ( Noyes 2003 ), Denmark ( Bakkendorf 1934 ), Finland ( Hellén 1974 ) [as
O. heterotomus
], Ireland ( Walker 1846 ), Norway ( Mathot 1969 ; Hellén 1974 ) [as
O. heterotomus
], and Romania ( Pricop 2008 ). NEARCTIC*: Canada *, USA * (including Alaska ).
